l18: $ b ÔŐó b $ by ax []
l19: $ _wff $ by not_elim [l14, l18]
l20: $ _wff $ by or_elim [l15, l17, l19]
l21: $ _ctx ÔŐó ┬Č (a ÔłĘ b) $ by not_intro [l20]
l22: $ _wff $ by imp_intro [l21]
-- Combine
l23: $ _wff $ by iff_intro [l11, l22]

